{"tid":873243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑不滿戴綠帽已婚男涉強姦律師女友   疑似第三者為已婚大狀","createTime":"2018-10-23T09:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T15:13:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2a634ec947d9a7566cd6f1781d2fb2335b81c68b","tid":873243,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181023/large/1540286678_243d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181023%2Flarge%2F1540286678_243d.jpg&h=51447251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已婚男商人涉嫌不滿年輕律師女友有第三者後提出分手，於是強迫女友口交及將她強姦。女事主X今繼續接受盤問，坦言與被告拍拖期間，被告雖已與妻子分居但仍有夫妻名份，故曾叫被告與妻子離婚，表示「希望可以係合適嘅時間，可以正式係一齊」。惟後來兩人分開，X被指結識了「第三者」蕭姓大律師，辯方透露蕭亦有家室，並育有兩名女兒，X表示知道。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳偉強（58歲）否認在2016年4至6月期間普通襲擊、非禮及強姦女事主X（33歲）。X稱曾叫被告離婚，辯方則指被告曾向X堅稱不會離婚，就算兩人拍拖期間，被告仍會於每個週末陪家人。X反駁，被告並非不願離婚，並稱「星期六同屋企人食晚飯好正常，我都會」。<br />\n<br />\n多輛名車以事主名字作車牌<br />\n<br />\n辯方呈上X與被告的合照及WhatsApp記錄作證，兩人於2013年開始拍拖，當時X仍未離婚，但已與同樣已婚的被告墮入熱戀，兩人亦以「老公老婆」相稱，X更以WhatsApp向被告表示自己從來不會說「I love you」，但對著被告則願意說。X同意。<br />\n<br />\n直到案發前數天，被告與X的WhatsApp對話仍然親暱，如X會叫被告做「豬」，並稱「我洗白白先喇」，及後又會互傳親吻的emoji。X則稱沒印象。<br />\n<br />\n另外，辯方指被告於2016年時擁有多達18輛汽車，當中包括名車勞斯萊斯、保時捷等，又指被告曾於2014年給X一輛保時捷代步。X否認，「只係借俾我駕一段時間」。辯方又指被告數輛名車均以X的英文名及姓氏作車牌，當中包括上述保時捷。X同意。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCCC30/18】"},{"pid":"aa6a0e2297facd65e1cc8d77ab0e81eb7fe92928","tid":873243,"uid":113000,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"專揀已婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b97220967b8bf12a616aa16bdd10fd518dc94e3","tid":873243,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa6a0e2297facd65e1cc8d77ab0e81eb7fe92928","tid":873243,"uid":113000,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"專揀已婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"保共黨好撚淫亂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d278a4d70c6df90f43e2274f80f92f3c3677154","tid":873243,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"真亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c5a97da9414e7fd2eabd14e0ed3ca94ec22fe5","tid":873243,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28309f55a9aad8cd5aa54d941227adff896eda1f","tid":873243,"uid":5489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"亂到諗起「最後每人射左兩次」個結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df70611104044b443cb3c3e876286c9d22a05ccb","tid":873243,"uid":810,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gs4fUwJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGs4fUwJ.png&h=d7859d88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6195a834e6b0729c967a38b71f8cb9738577220","tid":873243,"uid":211528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T10:52:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24584691d8a349e23022e13e2bc8ce323b133d0d","tid":873243,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa6a0e2297facd65e1cc8d77ab0e81eb7fe92928","tid":873243,"uid":113000,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T09:47:15.000Z","msg":"專揀已婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:34:37.000Z","msg":"終極臭雞<br />\n<br />\n好彩陳生識玩無俾你謀身家<br />\n<br />\n法律專業埋到身仲有淨？"},{"pid":"a7acbc82bde9aad178b742cffe303d915e4fd01c","tid":873243,"uid":64922,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T19:59:08.000Z","msg":"民賤聯<br />\n<